(v)  reviewing, and assessing or developing an organization strategy for institutional 
development of the NPPA; 
(vi)  providing quality control for all TA milestones and outputs; 
(vii)  developing a framework and business plan for the NPPA; 
(viii)  assessing and building the capacity of staff to undertake and sustain institutional 
